{
  "texts": [
    "The non-equilibrium molecular dynamics method (NEMD) was employed to establish the relation between the functionalization of silica surface and the interfacial thermal transport.",
    "Particularly, the heat flux through the interface and ITR were evaluated.",
    "The studied system is depicted in the Figure 1c.",
    "Similar to Klochko et al.",
    "45, the simulations were performed with periodic boundary conditions, while sufficient empty space was left in 𝑧 direction to prevent contact between the top and bottom silica slabs."
  ]
}